  "text": "Learning media have benefit toward learning process. One of those benefits is able to attract student's passion and makes learning interactive. Using correct learning media will make students accept study material easier. Besides that, correct learning media can be influencing students study result [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Alabdulkareem, 2015) .",
